Name: aspartame
Therapeutic effect: CAVE: Phenylketonuria, does not promote tooth decay
Metabolism: Aspartame is digested normally, breaks down to phenylalanine (CAVE Phenylketonuria), aspartic acid and a small amount of the organic compound methanol
